<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Will digital participation give us the cities we want?</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="5dcff5e8-3531-4fb9-a51a-ee2341e4d455">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/research/images/newsletter/2020-07/digital-participation-cities-0.jpg" alt="A digitally created image of a city, emphasizing technological infrastructure"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent empty">
	
</div>
						    
					
